{"tid":1607893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請各位行動人士特別係港島撚入，有個建議俾你哋","createTime":"2019-10-01T05:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T07:49:40.000Z","uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"371ee17c005cf60457a4c81a542947cf5fe0d4a3","tid":1607893,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"Sor, 冇建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64900a1e6f3687cc4daaf4097198914de9bc5f5","tid":1607893,"uid":113998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"On9少陣好冇"},{"pid":"40919ce24885fd51b89753fb3b92f1c47a163d50","tid":1607893,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"一路睇銅鑼灣遊行 我明白咗d野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efRQyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efRQyS</a>"},{"pid":"dea5600077d2c761e1af0fe5d08872f1bb1bc85a","tid":1607893,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日警察不斷恐嚇大家聽日唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，聽日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在明天閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"125de6c46e49fcecd018e4cfbac623dbeef1eeff","tid":1607893,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64900a1e6f3687cc4daaf4097198914de9bc5f5","tid":1607893,"uid":113998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"On9少陣好冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"Why？"},{"pid":"c911348ecbe2df23f5438d1301469a7e5028c51f","tid":1607893,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"<del>Sor, 冇建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1608095/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1608095/page/1</a><br />\n都係收收皮先"}]}